{"word":"ἰάλεμος","slug":"ἰάλεμος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἰάλεμος</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a wail, lament, dirge</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a>, <i>hapless, melancholy</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Prob. from the cry <el>ἰή.</el>\n"}]}